activities: Consumer data is collected from registered users for the purpose of providing health optimization services and general wellness features within our cafewell website. Our programs are designed to empower users to eat better, incorporate exercise, reduce stress, and look their best. Users are in control of their privacy though within their user profile. We utilize personal information to provide a tailor experience to them; communicate program information to the users; and to report progress toward any sponsored incentives.
